window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cupid, the God of Love, is no longer doing his job of creating romance. A disastrous mistake he’d made a quarter of a century ago forced him to put down his bow and arrow for good. </p> <p>Valentina Hart has never had any luck with men, and her last boyfriend was no prize by far. An unexpected meeting with a hot guy suddenly turns her sex life from non-existent to… DAMN. </p> <p>But, will Cupid’s secret drive Val away forever? Or will she stick around to show him what true and unconditional love really is?</p>"; 
